name: George Washington
ability: Sharply increases skill DMG by all team members when this daemon is Team Leader.
bond: Increases Forge Washington's skill DMG by 10%

additional_data.description: The spirit of the first US president. He values his country above all else, even himself, and devotes everything to it. He started spending more time with Forge after the copy incident blew over, passing on all sorts of lessons and making sure to spend more time in deep self-reflection. His manner has somehow grown more soft and relaxed than before. The two Washingtons look like brothers whenever they're together...which makes sense, considering they were originally the same person.
additional_data.how_to_acquire:
◦ "Chopping Trees? Stop, Please!" Event: Get a First Half Ranking of 2500 and above.
◦ "Chopping Trees? Stop, Please!" Event: Get a Second Half Ranking of 2500 and above.
◦ "Chopping Trees? Stop, Please!" Event: Get a Total Ranking of 5000 and above.
additional_data.notes_and_trivia: ◦ Slightly increases the total Event Points during the "Chopping Trees? Stop, Please!" event.

main: "If you keep at it long enough, most things eventually come true."
skill: "Evil must be destroyed. That is all."
summon: "I'll show you what it means to be great!"
limit_break: "Work long and hard enough, and anything will come true."
